---
// TechOverview.astro
import TechOverviewMobile from './TechOverviewMobile.tsx';
---

<section class="relative bg-zinc-50 overflow-visible selection:bg-black selection:text-white border-t border-zinc-200 text-black">
    
    <div class="hidden md:block py-24 md:py-40 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
            
            <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24 text-center px-6 reveal-up">
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-zinc-500 mb-6 block select-none" aria-hidden="true">/ NOSSO_PROCESSO</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-serif leading-[1.1] tracking-tighter">
                    Protocolo de <br /><span class="italic">desenvolvimento.</span>
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                
                <div class="group relative flex flex-col aspect-square border-2 border-black bg-white text-black reveal-up rounded-2xl overflow-hidden will-change-transform isolate-layer transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <div class="h-8 border-b border-black flex items-center px-4 gap-1.5 bg-zinc-100 group-hover:bg-black transition-colors duration-300">
                        <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/80"></div>
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80"></div>
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/80"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="ghost-label-extraction ml-auto font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-black/20 group-hover:text-white/40 transition-colors" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                        <h4 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold uppercase mb-4 text-inherit">Diagnóstico</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-70 font-sans mb-8">Nesta fase inicial, mergulhamos na arquitetura do seu modelo de negócio para identificar gargalos de conversão e oportunidades de escala. O resultado é um roadmap técnico e criativo desenhado para sustentar sua autoridade digital desde o primeiro dia.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-black/10 flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <div class="ghost-phase-01 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-black/20" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                            <div class="h-6 relative">
                                <span class="typewriter-text font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">[ MAPEANDO_OPORTUNIDADES ]</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative flex flex-col aspect-square border-2 border-black bg-white text-black reveal-up delay-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden will-change-transform isolate-layer transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <div class="h-8 border-b border-black flex items-center px-4 gap-1.5 bg-zinc-100 group-hover:bg-black transition-colors duration-300">
                        <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/80"></div>
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80"></div>
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/80"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="ghost-label-assembly ml-auto font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-black/20 group-hover:text-white/40 transition-colors" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                        <h4 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold uppercase mb-4 text-inherit">Desenvolvimento</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-70 font-sans mb-8">Trabalhamos na construção do ecossistema utilizando tecnologias de ponta como Next.js e Astro. Unimos o design de interface de alto impacto a um código limpo e escalável, garantindo que o seu ativo digital seja visualmente impecável e tecnicamente superior.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-black/10 flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <div class="ghost-phase-02 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-black/20" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                            <div class="h-6 relative">
                                <span class="typewriter-text font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">[ CRIANDO_SISTEMA_PROPRIETÁRIO ]</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative flex flex-col aspect-square border-2 border-black bg-white text-black reveal-up delay-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden will-change-transform isolate-layer transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <div class="h-8 border-b border-black flex items-center px-4 gap-1.5 bg-zinc-100 group-hover:bg-black transition-colors duration-300">
                        <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/80"></div>
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80"></div>
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/80"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="ghost-label-growth ml-auto font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-black/20 group-hover:text-white/40 transition-colors" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                        <h4 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold uppercase mb-4 text-inherit">Inteligência</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-70 font-sans mb-8">Finalizamos com a implementação de camadas de rastreamento e monitoramento de dados. Transformamos o site em um sistema dinâmico que fornece insights reais sobre o comportamento do seu cliente, permitindo otimizações constantes no seu ROI.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-black/10 flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <div class="ghost-phase-03 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-black/20" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                            <div class="h-6 relative">
                                <span class="typewriter-text font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">[ MONITORANDO_MÉTRICAS ]</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="mt-16 text-center opacity-10">
                <p class="technical-spec-footer font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.8em] text-black/20" aria-hidden="true"></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:hidden">
        <TechOverviewMobile client:visible />
    </div>

</section>

<style>
    @keyframes typewriter {
        from { width: 0; }
        to { width: 100%; }
    }

    .technical-spec-footer::after {
        content: 'TECHNICAL_SPEC_V1.1.0 // GRID_STABLE';
    }

    .ghost-label-extraction::after { content: '> STRATEGY_DECODE.LOG'; }
    .ghost-label-assembly::after { content: '> HIGH_FIDELITY_ENGINE.EXE'; }
    .ghost-label-growth::after { content: '> MONITOR_LOG.LOG'; }
    
    .ghost-phase-01::after { content: '[ FASE_01 ]'; }
    .ghost-phase-02::after { content: '[ FASE_02 ]'; }
    .ghost-phase-03::after { content: '[ FASE_03 ]'; }

    .will-change-transform { will-change: transform, opacity; }
    .isolate-layer { isolation: isolate; }
</style>